---
// HeroSection - main hero with title, description
---

<div class="relative lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-10">
  <div id="heading-home" class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1
      class="mt-5 text-4xl font-bold font-heading tracking-tight text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[3.5rem]"
    >
      Software Engineer and Web Developer.
    </h1>
    <div
      class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-base leading-[1.65rem] text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400"
    >
      <p>
        👋🏾 Hello, I'm
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white"
          >Christian Ludovic</span
        >, a software engineering student at Gümüşhane University of Technology.
        I am available for full-remote internship or part-time job opportunities.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build web applications using modern technologies like
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Laravel</span>,
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">React</span>,
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Vue.js</span>,
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Next.js</span> and
        <span class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Tailwind CSS</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
